    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢迎加入玩家社群和QQ官方群：314080642</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/a39ebbab527779928da33534c5b1e415.poster.avif?t=1741658415\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/a39ebbab527779928da33534c5b1e415.webm?t=1741658415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/a39ebbab527779928da33534c5b1e415.mp4?t=1741658415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演金探员，一位经验丰富的私家侦探，深入荒野，解开令人毛骨悚然的谜团。过去20年里，已有九人在一座诡异的别墅中神秘失踪，其中包括你最新委托人的亲属林先生。警方毫无进展，而解开这个恐怖谜题的重任落在了你肩上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/cd4de596ae33d342dd0c422d97e45a51.poster.avif?t=1741658415\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/cd4de596ae33d342dd0c422d97e45a51.webm?t=1741658415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/cd4de596ae33d342dd0c422d97e45a51.mp4?t=1741658415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你偷偷潜入别墅后，被不明物体击晕，醒来时发现自己被困在一间冰冷、凌乱的密室中。恐惧的气息弥漫四周，你意识到自己成为了这座诅咒别墅的最新囚徒。每个角落都隐藏着危险，丧尸在你身后步步紧逼，你必须争分夺秒逃出生天。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/d112ebb5746e56f9792e2334a757f986.poster.avif?t=1741658415\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/d112ebb5746e56f9792e2334a757f986.webm?t=1741658415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/d112ebb5746e56f9792e2334a757f986.mp4?t=1741658415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索别墅的黑暗走廊，揭开它阴森的过往，并拼凑出失踪案背后可怕的真相。找到隐藏的线索，解开复杂的谜题，并智取那些在庄园中游荡的不死生物。逃脱是你唯一的希望，否则你将成为这座诅咒别墅的又一个失踪者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/c9f711270a0af4ca5ad3c4fa32a57cba.poster.avif?t=1741658415\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/c9f711270a0af4ca5ad3c4fa32a57cba.webm?t=1741658415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/c9f711270a0af4ca5ad3c4fa32a57cba.mp4?t=1741658415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能活着逃出来，还是也会无声无息地消失？</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 日语, 韩语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 俄语, 简体中文, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 泰语, 繁体中文<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
